54.8	Liposuction	Liposuction	Liposuction, also known as lipoplasty ("fat modeling"), liposculpture suction lipectomy ("suction-assisted fat removal") or simply lipo is a cosmetic surgery operation that removes fat from many different sites on the human body. Areas affected can range from the abdomen, thighs and buttocks, to the neck, backs of the arms and elsewhere.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/19/Dr._Placik_Liposuction.jpg/230px-Dr._Placik_Liposuction.jpg
